16/08/2005
TIRANA, Albania -- A police spokesperson announced on Monday (15 August) the arrest of 40-year old Kujtim Vokshi, a suspect in a recent bank robbery. 
Earlier this month, $51,000 was stolen from a branch of the American Bank of Albania in downtown Tirana after four people broke into the bank and threatened staff and customers. 
Police reportedly found some of the stolen money in Vokshi's house. 
(Albanian News, Kathimerini - 16/08/05; AP, A1 TV - 15/08/05)
